## Decision Table

| Token Type | Namespace | How to Use |
|------------|-----------|------------|
| **Button height** | `--spacing-button-height-*` | `h-button-height-lg` |
| **Button padding** | `--spacing-button-padding-*` | `px-button-padding-x-lg` |
| **Button gap** | `--spacing-button-gap` | `gap-button-gap` |
| **Button radius** | `--radius-button` | `rounded-button` |
| **Button icon size** | `--spacing-button-icon-*` | `size-button-icon-lg` |
| **Colors** | `--color-*` (via config) | `bg-brand-accent` |
| **Typography** | Prefer `--text-*` if available | `text-*` (auto-generated) |

---

## When CSS Variable Syntax IS Needed

Only use `property-(--variable-name)` when:

### 1. Token is NOT in a valid namespace (and can't be renamed)

```jsx
'text-(length:--font-size-custom)'  // e.g. --font-size-* (not a theme namespace)
```

### 2. CSS calc() operations

```jsx
'rounded-[calc(var(--radius-xl)-1px)]'
'w-[calc(100%-var(--spacing-sidebar))]'
```

### 3. Complex CSS properties not covered by namespaces

```jsx
'animate-[fade-in_0.3s_ease-out]'
```

---

## Complete Namespace Reference

From [Tailwind v4 docs](https://tailwindcss.com/docs/theme#theme-variable-namespaces):

| Namespace | Generates These Utilities |
|-----------|--------------------------|
| `--color-*` | `bg-*`, `text-*`, `border-*`, `fill-*`, `stroke-*`, `ring-*`, etc. |
| `--spacing-*` | `p-*`, `m-*`, `gap-*`, `w-*`, `h-*`, `size-*`, `min-w-*`, `max-h-*`, etc. |
| `--radius-*` | `rounded-*` |
| `--shadow-*` | `shadow-*` |
| `--inset-shadow-*` | `inset-shadow-*` |
| `--drop-shadow-*` | `drop-shadow-*` |
| `--text-*` | `text-*` (font-size) |
| `--font-*` | `font-*` (font-family) |
| `--font-weight-*` | `font-*` (font-weight) |
| `--tracking-*` | `tracking-*` |
| `--leading-*` | `leading-*` |
| `--blur-*` | `blur-*` |
| `--ease-*` | `ease-*` |
| `--animate-*` | `animate-*` |
| `--breakpoint-*` | `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:` variants |

---

## Verification Checklist

Before submitting component code, verify:

1. **Component tokens use correct namespace** (`--spacing-*`, `--radius-*`, etc.)
2. **Using auto-generated utilities** (`h-button-height-lg`, not `h-(--spacing-button-height-lg)`)
3. **Colors use semantic classes** (`bg-brand-accent`, not `bg-[var(--color-*)]`)
4. **No `var()` syntax** unless calc() or non-namespace tokens

